cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper presents a new summarization dataset of news articles, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS) in the analysis and evaluation of the dataset.
